'''''The Millionaire Matchmaker''''' is an American [[reality television]] series on [[Bravo (U.S. TV channel)|Bravo]] that premiered on January 22, 2008, and is hosted by [[Patti Stanger]].<ref>{{cite press release|title=Bravo Sets a Date with Elite Matchmaker Patti Stanger in the Premiere of the New Docu-Drama 'The Millionaire Matchmaker,' Tuesday, January 22 at 11 PM|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2007/12/10/bravo-sets-a-date-with-elite-matchmaker-patti-stanger-in-the-premiere-of-the-new-docu-drama-the-millionaire-matchmaker-tuesday-january-22-at-11-pm--26184/20071210bravo01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|publisher=Futon Media|date=December 10, 2007|accessdate=January 11, 2013}}</ref> ''The Millionaire Matchmaker'' follows Patti Stanger, owner of the Beverly Hills-based "Millionaire's Club" dating service, as she matches single wealthy people with closely compatible dates.<ref>{{cite web|title=Marry rich with 'Millionaire Matchmaker'|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/life-style/marry-rich-millionaire-matchmaker-article-1.342302|work=[[New York Daily News]]|first=Gina|last=Salamone|accessdate=January 11, 2013|date=January 22, 2008}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mister. Lonely|date=January 20, 2008|url=https://nypost.com/2008/01/20/mister-lonely/|work=[[New York Post]]|accessdate=January 11, 2013|first=Paige|last=Albiniak}}</ref> The seventh season premiered on December 5, 2013, with an all-new panel of matchmakers.<ref name=Season7>{{cite press release|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|title=Bravo Media Premieres 'The Millionaire Matchmaker' at 9PM & New Series 'Courtney Loves Dallas' at 10PM on December 5|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/10/21/bravo-media-premieres-the-millionaire-matchmaker-at-9pm-new-series-courtney-loves-dallas-at-10pm-on-december-5/210387/|work=TV by the Numbers|date=October 21, 2013|accessdate=September 8, 2015|publisher=Tribune Digital Ventures}}</ref>

In July 2015, Stanger announced that she had left the network after eight seasons.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Harnick|first1=Chris|title=Patti Stanger Leaving Bravo After 8 Seasons of ''The Millionaire Matchmaker''|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/675008/patti-stanger-leaving-bravo-after-8-seasons-of-the-millionaire-matchmaker|work=[[E! Online]]|publisher=[[NBCUniversal]]|accessdate=July 10, 2015|location=United States|date=July 10, 2015}}</ref> It was later announced that she will be producing another show on [[WE tv]].<ref>{{cite press release|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|title=Millionaire Matchmaker Patti Stanger Joins WE tv|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/09/08/millionaire-matchmaker-patti-stanger-joins-we-tv/460446/|work=TV by the Numbers|publisher=Tribune Digital Ventures|date=September 8, 2015|accessdate=September 9, 2015}}</ref> The new series, entitled ''[[Million Dollar Matchmaker]]'', premiered on July 8, 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/05/31/patti-stanger-rmillion-dollar-matchmaker-we-tv|title=Patti Stanger returns in July with ''Million Dollar Matchmaker'' on WEtv|accessdate=July 4, 2016|date=May 31, 2016|first=Dan|last=Snierson|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]}}</ref>

''Millionaire'' followed the "pioneering" matchmaking show, [[Confessions of a Matchmaker]].<ref name="RyanLove">{{cite news |last1=Ryan |first1=Erin |title=‘America’s Matchmaker’ Patti Novak gives Vegas some tough love |url=https://lasvegasweekly.com/as-we-see-it/weekly-qa/2013/feb/22/americas-matchmaker-patti-novak-gives-vegas-some-t/ |accessdate=18 October 2018 |publisher=Las Vegas |date=22 February 2013}}</ref>

